title: 1stMate.Talk
body:
<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Captain>>
I've found this $CLUE. What can you tell me about it?
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<name|1stMate>>
<<Portrait|1stMate_neutral>>
Not much other than $Crew possessing greater knowledge over that than I.
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Captain>>
Thank you.
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<name|1stMate>>
Anytime.
<</Textbox>>

//End conversation
